The paper proposes a novel learning-aided scheme for sphere decoding in large MIMO systems. The use of a neural network for predicting minimum metrics and optimizing search order suggests a focus on information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG). The optimization of search radius and early termination scheme may also indicate a focus on control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the use of a neural network suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
